 - Wallpaper changer utility. 
Gif/jpg/html/bmp/..., can show web-pages and 
HTML and automatically apply special effect 
to the image (B&W/Opacity/Calendar/...) on 
the fly. Images can be grouped in themes. 
Every theme can have a weight -  which means 
how frequently it will be used. No 
'active desktop' requred. You will never see 
the same picture on your desktop! :)